"whole week in between, starting at the first day of the week (monday or "
"sunday, depending on your local settings)"
msgstr ""
"WEEKS(\"2002-19-02\"; \"2002-19-02\"; 1) zwraca 0, ponieważ nie ma pełnego "
"tygodnia pomiędzy datami"

